The evaluation on the symbols in the table is as follows :
○: faint and patchy parts are not observed on the handwriting as compared with the initial one and it has the same color density as that of the initial one;
×: faint and patchy parts are observed at the start of writing and the handwriting density is reduced as compared with the initial density.

